Biography:

"It's just me and my friends Dave and Alfredo who I've known for many years.  I've known Alfredo since I was 13 and we've waited until now to get together and see what happens. And the results were a lot of fun and we really like the record. Alfredo called me, we were all living in the desert at the time. I was living with Dave. Alfredo had just gotten off of the road with Queens Of The Stone Age and he gave me a call and said 'look man, I just left the band' and I said, 'oh wow, OK' and we chatted about that. I've lived with Dave for the last year and a and Dave is just an insane bass player.
